  <summary date="2021-04-01T20:42:52Z" status="Introduced in House">This resolution condemns all manifestations of expressions of racism and anti-Asian and Pacific Islander or ethnic intolerance.

The resolution calls on federal law enforcement officials, working with state and local officials, to

 expeditiously and vigorously investigate all reports of hate crimes and threats against Asian Americans and Pacific Islanders in the United States; work to improve the reporting of such hate crimes; and hold the perpetrators of those crimes, incidents, or threats accountable and bring the perpetrators to justice.</summary>
